<h2>Wishes Can Come True</h2>
<P ALIGN="center"><STRONG><BR><STRONG>Wishes Can Come True</STRONG></STRONG></P>  <P><BR><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/images/maw/P1010078_lo.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010078.jpg"></A>Patrick
  Baldwin made a wish. As a 13 year old fighting a battle against Muscular
  Dystrophy, the Make-A-Wish Foundation&reg; stood ready to grant almost any
  wish to the young man. If he desired, Patrick could have met a celebrity,
  taken a trip to anywhere in the world, or become a radio disc jockey just to
  name a few. However, Patrick didn't want any of that. He wanted to hunt
  dragons.</P>  <P>The Make-A-Wish Foundation was founded in 1980 as a means to grant
  children with life-threatening illnesses a way to realize their dreams. This
  charitable organization has made the wishes of more than 80,000 children come
  true in the past twenty years. This year, Make-A-Wish made Patrick Baldwin's
  dream to meet the developers of EverQuest&reg; a reality.<BR><BR><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/images/P1010020_lo.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010020.jpg"></A>Patrick beamed
  as he buzzed across the Sony Online Entertainment parking lot, his parents in
  tow. In just a few short minutes, he would meet Brad McQuaid, Jeff Butler,
  Gordon Wrinn and the rest of the development team behind his favorite game,
  EverQuest.</P>  <P>The EverQuest Live studio occupies the second floor of SOE's Game
  Development building where work on the third expansion, The Shadows of
  Luclin&#8482;, continues. This is where Patrick found himself shortly after
  his arrival. Following introductions to the various members of the EQ Live
  team, Gordon Wrinn invited Patrick into his office and treated him to an in-game
  tour of the completed parts of the Luclin expansion. While Gordon explained
  aspects of the in-game action, Brad and Jeff provided commentary on the
  Luclin back-story and why they made certain decisions in the design.</P>  <P><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/images/P1010047_lo.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010047.jpg"></A>During lunch,
  Patrick met Firiona Vie, portrayed by Denise Harris, who presented to him an
  EverQuest poster autographed by herself and fantasy artist Keith Parkinson.
  SOE's artist Ken Meyer also gave Patrick several pieces of memorabilia,
  including a portrait of his in-game character painted by Ken; an over-sized
  greeting card with illustrations by the EQ team, the concept drawing of the
  Luclin Vacuum Worm; an illustration by Rick Johnson of an Iksar and many
  other EQ related items. After lunch, Patrick packed up his loot and a special
  dragon raid commenced on the test server.</P>  <P>The heroes gathered, names of those not often seen fighting in game
  against Norrath's creatures: Aradune, Ifurita, Firiona Vie, Lady Daegarmo,
  Mennix, Lady Madera, Dartok, and countless other characters belonging to
  members of the EverQuest team joined Patrick's character and rushed to slay
  the Sleeper. After a hard fought 90 minutes of battle, the last of the heroes
  fell to the warders. Corpses littered the ground in-game, and a sense of
  excitement filled the air in the office. Even though the raid saw the deaths
  of every character present, the gleam in Patrick's eyes proved its success.</P>  <P><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/images/P10100996_lo.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010996.jpg"></A>Patrick's day
  was not finished. To cap off his wish, he was introduced to Sam Powell, SOE's
  Sound Engineer. Sam had Patrick lay down some special effect sounds and
  voice-overs for inclusion in the Luclin expansion. Now, when players get the
  chance to explore the Shadows of Luclin, they will be able to experience the
  sound stylings of Patrick Baldwin forever linking this extraordinary young
  man to his wish.</P>  <P>Patrick made his wish, and that wish came true. Because of organizations
  like the Make-A-Wish Foundation, children with life-threatening illness get
  the chance to smile and to know that they are never alone in facing their
  afflictions. For more information on how to help a child's wish come true,
  visit the <A HREF="http://www.wish.org/">Make-A-Wish Foundation's web site</A>.</P>  <P><BR>-Steve Fuller (<A HREF="mailto:sfuller@station.sony.com">sfuller@station.sony.com</A>)</P>  <TABLE STYLE="width:80.0%;mso-cellspacing:0in;mso-padding-alt:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes"><TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/EQ00051.jpg"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/images/EQ000051_lo.jpg"></A></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/EQ00131.jpg"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/images/EQ000131_lo.jpg"></A></P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:1"><TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/EQ00116.jpg"></A></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/EQ00090.jpg"></A></P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:2"><TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010098.jpg"></A></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010084.jpg"></A></P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:3;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes"><TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010070.jpg"></A></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt"><P ALIGN="center"><A HREF="../../../../../community/images/P1010028.jpg"></A></P></TD></TR></TABLE>  <P>&nbsp;</P>



